review:
After completing my braces treatment,
I am extremely happy with my teeth and now I can smile with confidence!. Thank you so much Dr kishor for all the professional advice and care you have shown over the last few years..

I would strongly recommend Kishor's Dentistry for all your dental treatments.
I did teeth cleaning and polishing as I had sever tooth discoloration and was highly uncomfortable before the treatment.now happy
It was a great experience with Dr Preethi. I had root canal for my teeth and no pain during treatment
I had severe tooth discolored.  I wanted to place zirconia crown and doctor recommend teeth whitening for single rooth and happy
I visited Dr Preethi for general consultation of my teeth as I had severe gum problems . Doctors adviced flap surgery and happy with the treatment
I visited Dr kishore dentistry to consult Dr Preethi for my tooth ache and she suggested rct for my teeth .happy
I started my invisalign treatment for my tooth spacing in between teeth and happy with the result . Thak you
I had tooth ache and started my rct immediately as Dr Preethi adviced to save my teeth with post and crown. Thank you Dr kishors dentistry team
Chennai well established dental clinic for all kind of oral treatment like braces , RCT and Invisalign.
I had a teeth pain and I wanted to remove the teeth but doctor recommended to do root canal treatment. Thank you
